01:40:19.736 --> 01:40:21.343
PLEASE SHRI VISHNUMAYA,

01:40:21.544 --> 01:40:26.110
DESTROY THE EVIL FORCES THAT
MATERIALISM CREATED.

01:40:26.311 --> 01:40:30.551
Om Twameva Sakshat

01:40:30.752 --> 01:40:38.947
