is thereby reduced to slavery.

01:41:30.219 --> 01:41:31.965
PLEASE SHRI RADHA,

01:41:32.166 --> 01:41:36.732
DESTROY THE EVIL FORCES THAT
MATERIALISM CREATED.

01:41:36.933 --> 01:41:41.168
Om Twameva Sakshat

